Casting: Manoj Krishna Tanneru, Darshini Sekhar, Indu madhavi, Ravi Siva Teja Paila, Raghav Indra, Uday Tej, Karthik Venkata, Anirudh AJ, Srilekha Samudrala, Gautami Krishnan, Harin Chandra, 

A Srinivas & Sivasai Writings 
Dialogues & Directed by : SivaSai Vardhan Jaladhanki, 
DOP: Kamal Nabh, Sreedhar Kv, 
Music: Jagdeesh Satyan, 
Lyrics: Bhaskarabhatla Ravikumar Garu & Basha
Editing & DI : Nani Lukka, 
Publicity design: Bsp Roy, 
Dubbing : Swathi Musti,
BGM : PVR Raja
Department: Basha Sha Meheboob, Chiranjeevi Gopisetty, Artiste Durgaji Yedida 
Location Courtesy: Anirudh AJ, Aparna Bulusu 
Line Producers: Sriharsha Basava, Karthik
Marketing- Anil, Bhavya Natasha
Production: Padma
Producers: Saideep Reddy Borra , Rahul Tamada
